{"tid":1638210,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"教育局今日致電中學查詢戴口罩學生人數 有校長回覆：沒特別留意","createTime":"2019-10-08T08:43:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T09:05:15.000Z","uid":212626,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9f15f1d581e5310fd32b2de616b020be641b0b88","tid":1638210,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T08:43:42.000Z","msg":"教育局早前要求中學今天十一時前，提供戴口罩的學生人數等資料。<br />\n<br />\n有中學回覆本台查詢時指，並沒主動上報資料，至下午接獲教育局分區人員致電查詢，該校校長回覆對方指：<span style=\"color: red;\">「沒特別留意。」</span><br />\n<br />\n亦有中學校表示，已向教育局報告有「少部分學生帶口罩」，但沒有提供確實人數。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/RTHKVNEWS/photos/a.723529797755079/2865385576902813/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FRTHKVNEWS%2Fphotos%2Fa.723529797755079%2F2865385576902813%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=NaStGCRJdOSKaO4BfYueNsWiAETkOtN%2FvKUl8N5Dwlc%3D&h=35cecab4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/RTHKVNEWS/photos/a.723529797755079/2865385576902813/?type=3&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"5914176a16fd25c1496696e4c532976203a556dd","tid":1638210,"uid":270863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f15f1d581e5310fd32b2de616b020be641b0b88","tid":1638210,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T08:43:42.000Z","msg":"教育局早前要求中學今天十一時前，提供戴口罩的學生人數等資料。<br />\n<br />\n有中學回覆本台查詢時指，並沒主動上報資料，至下午接獲教育局分區人員致電查詢，該校校長回覆對方指：<span style=\"color: red;\">「沒特別留意。」</span><br />\n<br />\n亦有中學校表示，已向教育局報告有「少部分學生帶口罩」，但沒有提供確實人數。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/RTHKVNEWS/photos/a.723529797755079/2865385576902813/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FRTHKVNEWS%2Fphotos%2Fa.723529797755079%2F2865385576902813%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=NaStGCRJdOSKaO4BfYueNsWiAETkOtN%2FvKUl8N5Dwlc%3D&h=35cecab4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/RTHKVNEWS/photos/a.723529797755079/2865385576902813/?type=3&amp;theater</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T11